    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate the <strong>parsnips</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated parsnip </strong>to the middle of a<strong> tea towel </strong>and bring the four corners together to form a ball, twist the ball and squeeze out as much liquid as you can</p><p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> grated cheese </strong>and<strong> grated parsnip </strong>to a bowl with the<strong> honey</strong>,<strong> </strong>a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>cheesy parsnip</strong></p>",
